"_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-nh%E1%BA%A1c/poem-EpzWfGVBH2wEhP3RsbFZjA">Thanh bình nhạc - 清平樂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/author-kEtJEG_ZpvOqTp5qubCKUQ">Hạ Chú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/T%E1%BB%91ng-ph%C3%B2-m%C3%A3-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-V%C4%83n-huynh/poem-JvWJsuOnXmnUzS8pq3KQVA">Tống phò mã Thiếu Văn huynh - 送駙馬少文兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/author-l-vfhV6KqRexQyEkpib8Ng">Đặng Huy Trứ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%E1%BB%A8c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Ức đệ kỳ 1 - 憶弟其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Chi/V%E1%BB%8Dng-gia-th%C6%B0/poem-Q0TAkuuOaVash8qnVD-2lA">Vọng gia thư - 望家書</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Chi/author-PDwspC721eAeaL3MOQf-eA">Lý Chi</a>)<br></div>	</div>
